[11:34] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'is already set up and works out of the box. The security is already there, credential management, remote access, it all just works. The MCP makes the connection between tools like Claude Code and N8N. So, Claude Code can'

[11:47] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'directly interact with N8N like it\'s a user right in the UI. Without the MCP, Claude can\'t actually change or see anything in your N8N instance. The N8N skills and all skills are just extra'

[12:01] [scene:talk]
